 Reference List.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Reference list<\\/strong> should appear at the end of the document, arranged in alphabetical order, using the second name of the author, or of the first author in case of multiple authors. See the following examples. <em>COMPLETE and ACCURATE references are required <\\/em>including page span of the article or chapter. Accurate and current URLs and\\/or DOI\\u2019s are required where relevant, including latest access date for all URLs cited. Reference entries should follow a consistent standard format. Thesis writing guides explain this in detail. TJPSD\\u2019s house format follows in the examples below; it is best to follow these examples when constructing and proofreading your reference list before submitting your final draft:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ol start=\\"8\\">\\r\\n<li><em>TJPSD <\\/em>is a peer reviewed journal. Articles submitted for publication are reviewed by <strong>at least two referees anonymously who remain unaware of the author(s) or the affiliation of the author(s)<\\/strong>, and who are experts or well-read in the respective subject. Blind reviews are fundamental and decisive in determining acceptance or rejection of a manuscript.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Copyright<\\/strong>: It is a condition of publication that authors vest copyright of their articles, including abstracts, in <em>TJPSD<\\/em>. This enables the editors to ensure full copyright protection and to disseminate the article, and the journal, to the widest possible readership in print and electronic formats as appropriate. Authors may, of course, use the published article elsewhere under permission from the Chief Editor.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>As of June 2018, <em>TJPSD <\\/em>will be available online, this includes all back issues. Issues are uploaded as soon as they are paged in production, shortly prior to the release of the hard copy versions from the printer.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>For further information and contributions, please contact<\\/strong>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Chief Editor<\\/strong>, <strong><em>TJPSD<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>College of Social Sciences,<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Population Studies and Research Centre<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>University of Dar es Salaam,<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>P.O. Box 35047,<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dar es Salaam, TANZANIA.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>E-mail: <a href=\\"mailto:psrc@udsm.ac,tz\\">psrc@udsm.ac,tz<\\/a>\\u2013 the official email is unfortunately unreliable<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Editor\\u2019s email: <a href=\\"mailto:hhambati2020@gmail.com\\">hhambati2020@gmail.com<\\/a> \\u2013 this email is secure and recommended<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Editor\\u2019s Phone: +255-784-452-028<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Chief Editor<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Prof. Herbert Hambati<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Guidelines to Authors"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]}]},{"_data":{"id":55,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":18,"parentId":0,"seq":6},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":18,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_ABOUT","path":"","titleLocaleKey":"navigation.about","content":{"en_US":""}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[{"_data":{"id":56,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":19,"parentId":18,"seq":7},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":19,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_ABOUT","titleLocaleKey":"about.aboutContext"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]},{"_data":{"id":57,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":20,"parentId":18,"seq":8},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":20,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_SUBMISSIONS","titleLocaleKey":"about.submissions"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]},{"_data":{"id":58,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":21,"parentId":18,"seq":9},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":21,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_EDITORIAL_TEAM","titleLocaleKey":"about.editorialTeam"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]},{"_data":{"id":59,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":29,"parentId":18,"seq":10},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":29,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"policy","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>POLICY of <em>Tanzanian Journal of Population Studies and Development<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Population Studies and Research Centre (PSRC)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>University of Dar es Salaam<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Upon submission of an accepted manuscript (post-review) the author is asked to submit a <em>signed<\\/em> statement formally declaring that publication of the article by <em>TJPSD<\\/em> would not contravene any copyright or other contractual agreements relevant to the article or the research upon which it is based. This requires that the article is not already published, nor in press, nor under consideration for any other publication where acceptance and publication is anticipated. It also requires that all copyright protocols to works cited, used, paraphrased and quoted have been duly observed by the author(s) appearing within the manuscript to be published by <em>TJPSD<\\/em>.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n<li><strong> POLICY <\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<p><em>TJPSD<\\/em> is devoted to articles and research information on Tanzania and East Africa primarily, the global South and elsewhere in general. Our subject is to explain what takes place in our social, personal, legal, political, natural, economic, fertility, mortality, bioethical, migration and natural and human made environments, why and how; achievements and challenges in research and development efforts and possible problem-solving alternatives. We are particularly interested in work done which critiques, challenges, corrects or jettisons the flaws recognised in standard, conventional, fashionable assumptions and frameworks for addressing enduring concerns and matters arising on the African continent and global in general.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>TJPSD <\\/em>is not bound by narrow confines of disciplines. We welcome articles on themes and topics covering the broad spectrum of social sciences and humanities, including geography, history, economics, education, development studies, planning, social administration, literature, statistics, philosophy, cultural studies, religious studies, and law, to mention just a few. People of different ideological standpoints have the opportunity to argue their positions and cases, and we do welcome such healthy debates without taking part, to allow and promote complete academic freedom.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Editorial Team <em>TJPSD<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"TJPSD Policy"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]},{"_data":{"id":60,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":22,"parentId":18,"seq":11},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":22,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_PRIVACY","titleLocaleKey":"manager.setup.privacyStatement"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]},{"_data":{"id":61,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":25,"parentId":18,"seq":12},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":25,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"subscription","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Subscription<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Africa: US$ 8<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Rest of the World: US$ 16<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Single copies can be purchased at US$ 8 for Africa; and US$ 20 for the rest of the world.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Send your orders to:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>The Chief Editor<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tanzania Journal of Population Studies and Development<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>University of Dar es Salaam<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>P.O. Box 35047<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dar es Salaam<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>TANZANIA<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>E-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\\"mailto:dtu@uccmail.ac.tz\\">psrc@udsm.ac.tz<\\/a><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Subscription"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]}]},{"_data":{"id":62,"menuId":3,"menuItemId":23,"parentId":0,"seq":13},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItem":{"_data":{"id":23,"contextId":1,"type":"NMI_TYPE_CONTACT","titleLocaleKey":"about.contact"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false,"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false},"children":[]}]}';